1
00:00:13,260 --> 00:00:14,860
I heard from Jing that

2
00:00:15,180 --> 00:00:16,860
you both like art exhibitions.

3
00:00:17,939 --> 00:00:18,739
Yes, auntie.

4
00:00:19,899 --> 00:00:21,460
I don't mean anything else.

5
00:00:22,180 --> 00:00:23,620
I just think

6
00:00:23,620 --> 00:00:25,219
you and Jing

7
00:00:25,579 --> 00:00:26,899
are a better match.

8
00:00:27,379 --> 00:00:28,860
One is gentle and generous,

9
00:00:29,219 --> 00:00:30,580
the other is well-behaved and sensible.

10
00:00:30,900 --> 00:00:32,300
And you have a common topic.

11
00:00:33,620 --> 00:00:34,459
What do you think?

12
00:00:38,540 --> 00:00:39,379
Let's eat.

13
00:00:42,779 --> 00:00:44,300
Okay, I'm on my way.

14
00:00:45,260 --> 00:00:46,540
Why are you here?

15
00:00:48,379 --> 00:00:50,660
Xiaoxue, I just made an appointment with my doctor.

16
00:00:50,660 --> 00:00:51,660
Let's go now.

17
00:00:51,819 --> 00:00:52,459
Okay.

18
00:00:52,980 --> 00:00:54,260
Please help me pack up the materials

19
00:00:54,340 --> 00:00:55,340
and the laptop on the table.

20
00:00:57,660 --> 00:00:58,179
Come on.

21
00:00:58,980 --> 00:01:00,059
Don't let them know

22
00:01:00,059 --> 00:01:01,139
I can't see now.

23
00:01:07,579 --> 00:01:08,340
Young Master Yan,

24
00:01:08,620 --> 00:01:10,219
we can't confirm

25
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:11,540
the cause of your temporary blindness

26
00:01:11,540 --> 00:01:12,779
at the moment.

27
00:01:13,180 --> 00:01:14,740
We'll try to find out the cause as soon as possible.

28
00:01:14,740 --> 00:01:15,820
In the meantime,

29
00:01:15,980 --> 00:01:17,859
don't take any medication.

30
00:01:18,180 --> 00:01:18,859
Remember.

31
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:31,980
The doctor said it's temporary.

32
00:01:31,980 --> 00:01:33,299
Don't worry too much.

33
00:01:33,620 --> 00:01:35,100
Now the acquisition deal has hit a snag,

34
00:01:36,460 --> 00:01:37,900
and my eyes have gone blind again.

35
00:01:40,419 --> 00:01:41,700
Don't be too anxious.

36
00:01:43,419 --> 00:01:45,019
I'm here, it's okay.

37
00:01:47,260 --> 00:01:48,779
I'll go make you a cup of coffee first.

38
00:01:49,579 --> 00:01:50,260
Okay.

39
00:02:01,380 --> 00:02:02,059
Xiaoxue,

40
00:02:02,059 --> 00:02:02,900
now only Ji Xiaoxue

41
00:02:02,900 --> 00:02:04,740
can enter this room, right?

42
00:02:16,980 --> 00:02:19,019
Now you see only Ji Xiaoxue,

43
00:02:21,739 --> 00:02:23,820
and you don't even want to talk to me, right?

44
00:02:25,260 --> 00:02:25,980
What's the matter?

45
00:02:27,899 --> 00:02:28,500
The contract

46
00:02:28,940 --> 00:02:29,780
needs your signature.

47
00:02:33,500 --> 00:02:35,380
You did this on purpose, didn't you?

48
00:02:37,339 --> 00:02:38,260
What do you mean?

49
00:02:38,700 --> 00:02:40,700
I mean, you brought this up again,

50
00:02:40,980 --> 00:02:41,820
didn't you?

51
00:02:41,940 --> 00:02:44,339
Now, the pressure is on your proposal.

52
00:02:44,780 --> 00:02:46,700
I need to come up with a plan to divert attention.

53
00:02:46,940 --> 00:02:48,299
The board has approved this.

54
00:02:48,299 --> 00:02:49,859
Since you came to our Gu family,

55
00:02:50,700 --> 00:02:52,419
there has been a problem with the acquisition.

56
00:02:53,459 --> 00:02:55,700
It was a good project for business expansion.

57
00:02:56,179 --> 00:02:57,660
Now it has become a burden.

58
00:02:58,700 --> 00:02:59,899
Wasn't it you?

59
00:03:00,940 --> 00:03:02,139
And the marriage between our two families

60
00:03:02,139 --> 00:03:03,419
was also proposed by you.

61
00:03:04,100 --> 00:03:05,339
What exactly is your purpose?

62
00:03:09,139 --> 00:03:09,980
Gu Chengyan,

63
00:03:10,619 --> 00:03:12,660
the marriage was indeed proposed by our Xia family.

64
00:03:13,459 --> 00:03:15,660
But that was my dad's choice

65
00:03:15,660 --> 00:03:16,660
because of the stock price fluctuation

66
00:03:16,660 --> 00:03:17,820
caused by your father's death.

67
00:03:18,859 --> 00:03:20,660
We do have business cooperation.

68
00:03:20,980 --> 00:03:22,619
You can also think that we are protecting ourselves.

69
00:03:23,179 --> 00:03:24,179
But your father's death

70
00:03:24,179 --> 00:03:26,179
should have a greater impact on your family.

71
00:03:26,619 --> 00:03:27,459
And how could our family

72
00:03:27,459 --> 00:03:29,019
marry me to your family

73
00:03:29,019 --> 00:03:30,660
for such a small matter?

74
00:03:32,260 --> 00:03:33,139
Gu Chengyan,

75
00:03:33,820 --> 00:03:35,700
if you think I'm messing with you

76
00:03:36,100 --> 00:03:37,380
or your family,

77
00:03:38,100 --> 00:03:39,100
I'll leave now.

78
00:03:41,419 --> 00:03:42,500
I'm sorry, Miss Xia.

79
00:03:42,780 --> 00:03:43,780
It's just that Young Master Yan

80
00:03:43,780 --> 00:03:44,940
is too upset about this.

81
00:03:44,940 --> 00:03:45,739
Shut up.

82
00:03:46,579 --> 00:03:47,619
If it weren't for you,

83
00:03:47,820 --> 00:03:48,940
would he treat me like this?

84
00:03:56,060 --> 00:03:56,700
Wanqing,

85
00:03:59,579 --> 00:04:00,820
I've been too much lately.

86
00:04:01,660 --> 00:04:02,419
I'm sorry.

87
00:04:03,100 --> 00:04:04,100
I shouldn't have said that.

88
00:04:05,540 --> 00:04:06,220
Xiaoxue,

89
00:04:06,859 --> 00:04:07,700
give me the pen.

90
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:29,339
Miss Xia,

91
00:04:35,060 --> 00:04:36,459
I hope this is the first

92
00:04:37,700 --> 00:04:38,740
and last time.

93
00:04:39,700 --> 00:04:40,459
Otherwise,

94
00:04:41,139 --> 00:04:42,459
I will definitely cancel the marriage.

95
00:04:49,860 --> 00:04:50,459
By the way,

96
00:04:51,659 --> 00:04:53,740
the chairman of the exhibition will go to the art gallery today

97
00:04:54,019 --> 00:04:55,099
and wants to hear your plan.

98
00:05:08,700 --> 00:05:09,620
The art gallery

99
00:05:09,620 --> 00:05:11,979
should highlight the uniqueness of art

100
00:05:11,979 --> 00:05:13,620
and its value in the era.

101
00:05:13,740 --> 00:05:16,339
We should avoid being similar to other galleries

102
00:05:16,659 --> 00:05:18,099
so as to give visitors

103
00:05:18,099 --> 00:05:19,420
a brand-new feeling.

104
00:05:19,620 --> 00:05:20,180
Good.

105
00:05:20,339 --> 00:05:21,979
I think it's a good idea.

106
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:24,820
But we also have to follow

107
00:05:24,820 --> 00:05:26,180
the aesthetic of the people now,

108
00:05:26,180 --> 00:05:27,339
thus improving

109
00:05:27,339 --> 00:05:29,659
the quality and level of the exhibition hall design.

110
00:05:29,659 --> 00:05:32,060
Yes, it's very in line with the modern understanding of art.

111
00:05:32,219 --> 00:05:32,979
Good idea.

112
00:05:40,260 --> 00:05:41,579
Do you remember this art gallery?

113
00:05:57,740 --> 00:05:58,500
I didn't expect

114
00:05:58,940 --> 00:06:00,459
you to have so many ideas about the art gallery.

115
00:06:00,579 --> 00:06:01,019
No.

116
00:06:01,019 --> 00:06:01,779
Sorry.

117
00:06:05,339 --> 00:06:06,219
Let's go.

118
00:06:20,420 --> 00:06:20,940
Right.

119
00:06:22,380 --> 00:06:23,659
I am indeed blind.

120
00:06:24,820 --> 00:06:25,620
How could this happen?

121
00:06:28,659 --> 00:06:29,979
Since you are blind,

122
00:06:30,500 --> 00:06:32,579
you should give up your position as the heir.

123
00:06:33,060 --> 00:06:35,099
With your current physical condition,

124
00:06:35,420 --> 00:06:37,099
you can't manage the company at all.

125
00:06:38,380 --> 00:06:39,539
I am blind,

126
00:06:40,500 --> 00:06:41,940
but some people are heart-blind.

127
00:06:46,380 --> 00:06:48,019
Do you really think that just because I'm blind,

128
00:06:49,060 --> 00:06:49,979
I'm going to...

129
00:06:49,979 --> 00:06:50,579
Watch out!

130
00:06:58,060 --> 00:06:59,339
I'm going to fall?

131
00:07:00,860 --> 00:07:01,620
Xiaoxue,

132
00:07:02,620 --> 00:07:03,339
let's go.

133
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:25,019
The test shows

134
00:07:25,219 --> 00:07:27,300
there are other chemical components in the medicine.

135
00:07:27,300 --> 00:07:29,139
Long-term use can cause blindness,

136
00:07:29,300 --> 00:07:31,659
but stopping the medication will lead to recovery.

137
00:07:34,019 --> 00:07:35,260
This is the new medicine I prescribed for him.

138
00:07:36,019 --> 00:07:37,180
He only needs to take one pill.

139
00:07:37,300 --> 00:07:38,380
he shouldn't have any resistance.

140
00:07:39,740 --> 00:07:41,219
Has my brother been taking his medicine on time?

141
00:07:41,420 --> 00:07:42,979
I secretly put the medicine in his liquor.

142
00:07:42,979 --> 00:07:44,139
This way, he won't find out.

143
00:07:48,979 --> 00:07:49,659
Remember,

144
00:07:50,620 --> 00:07:51,940
you'll always be mine.

145
00:07:52,860 --> 00:07:54,060
You can only listen to me.

146
00:07:55,500 --> 00:07:57,139
I didn't expect you to treat your brother like this.

147
00:07:58,180 --> 00:08:00,139
Don't you know this medicine has side effects?

148
00:08:05,019 --> 00:08:06,779
I didn't know this medicine had side effects either.

149
00:08:07,979 --> 00:08:09,380
How could you not know?

150
00:08:09,940 --> 00:08:11,380
People of your status

151
00:08:11,380 --> 00:08:12,060
must undergo strict drug tests

152
00:08:12,060 --> 00:08:14,579
for all medications.

153
00:08:15,180 --> 00:08:17,620
You make me give him medicine every day and you don't know?

154
00:08:18,659 --> 00:08:19,380
Xiaoxue,

155
00:08:20,459 --> 00:08:21,420
you don't believe me?

156
00:08:22,380 --> 00:08:23,060
Didn't you say

157
00:08:23,060 --> 00:08:24,579
you would do anything for me?

158
00:08:24,860 --> 00:08:26,620
That's because I thought you loved me.

159
00:08:27,820 --> 00:08:28,779
I love you too.

160
00:08:29,300 --> 00:08:30,499
I still love you now.

161
00:08:30,499 --> 00:08:31,739
You don't love me at all.

162
00:08:32,700 --> 00:08:34,140
You've been using me.

163
00:08:34,140 --> 00:08:36,140
You've been using me from the beginning.

164
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:49,180
You're like this because you love my brother?
